vote.title: An ordinance granting renewal of a revocable license to Frankie’s Downtown LLC, for the use of approximately 405 square feet of land to , occupy and maintain an existing sidewalk cafe and eight wooden planters on a portion of Main Street right-of-way located near its intersection with Field Street - Revenue: General Fund $200.00 annually and a $100.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
